::Prowl::

Prowl sees Hot Rod walk by, and jogs to catch up with him. He would 
find IR and apologize later, when he thought of a way to fix what he 
did.

"Hey, Hot Rod!" he says as he approaches the other Maximal, "Iron 
Raptor said for us to wait outside by the city. She's got something 
planned."
